username-recon
==============

This plugin re-implements the username-enumeration technique popularized by the
Sherlock Project. The detection engine (hunt.py) is original, dependency-free
code written for this plugin.

The bundled site manifest (skills/username-search/data/data.json) is derived from
the Sherlock Project's community-maintained site list, which is distributed under
the MIT License.

  Sherlock Project — https://github.com/sherlock-project/sherlock
  Copyright (c) Sherlock Project contributors
  Licensed under the MIT License.

Use `hunt.py update` to refresh the manifest from the upstream community list.

This plugin is intended for lawful, authorized use only: checking your own
accounts, consented investigations, security research, and brand/impersonation
monitoring. Respect each site's Terms of Service and rate limits.
